'Defined by I. R. Pagnossin (6.7.2007)
Function Lorentz( x, y, x0, y0, A, W, z0 )
Lorentz = 2 * A * W / (3.1415 * (4*(x-x0)^2 + 4*(y-y0)^2 + W^2)) + z0
End Function

'Defined by I. R. Pagnossin (6.7.2007)
Function Heaviside( x )
If( x > 0 ) Then
  Heaviside = 1
Else
  If( x < 0 ) Then
    Heaviside = 0
  Else
    Heaviside = 0.5
  End If
End If
End Function